  <brief_title>Chest Shielding in Premature Infants During Phototherapy</brief_title>
  <acronym>SLIGHT</acronym>
  <official_title>Effect of Chest Shielding on the Incidence of Patent Ductus Arteriosus in Premature Infants Undergoing Phototherapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
